### ShipRoutesX example requests
### Works with the VS Code "REST Client" extension or JetBrains' built-in
### HTTP client — click "Send Request" above any block. Requires
### `npm run dev` running (see ../installation.md).

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3041

### Service metadata
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Liveness check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Graph stats for the default (20km) resolution
GET {{baseUrl}}/graph/stats

### Graph stats for a specific resolution
GET {{baseUrl}}/graph/stats?resolutionKm=50

### Basic route: Marseille -> Shanghai
POST {{baseUrl}}/route
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "origin": { "lat": 43.3, "lng": 5.3 },
  "destination": { "lat": 31.2, "lng": 121.8 }
}

### Same route, avoiding the Suez Canal — routes via Cape of Good Hope instead
POST {{baseUrl}}/route
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "origin": { "lat": 43.3, "lng": 5.3 },
  "destination": { "lat": 31.2, "lng": 121.8 },
  "options": { "avoid": ["suez"] }
}

### Same route, over the 50km network
POST {{baseUrl}}/route
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "origin": { "lat": 43.3, "lng": 5.3 },
  "destination": { "lat": 31.2, "lng": 121.8 },
  "options": { "resolutionKm": 50 }
}

### Los Angeles -> New York via the Panama Canal
POST {{baseUrl}}/route
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "origin": { "lat": 33.7, "lng": -118.25 },
  "destination": { "lat": 40.7, "lng": -74.0 }
}

### Invalid coordinate -> 400 ROUTE_VALIDATION_ERROR
POST {{baseUrl}}/route
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "origin": { "lat": 999, "lng": 5.3 },
  "destination": { "lat": 31.2, "lng": 121.8 }
}

### Recognized but unavailable resolution -> 400 NETWORK_UNAVAILABLE
POST {{baseUrl}}/route
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "origin": { "lat": 43.3, "lng": 5.3 },
  "destination": { "lat": 31.2, "lng": 121.8 },
  "options": { "resolutionKm": 10 }
}

### The OpenAPI spec itself
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi.json
